00:11:23.220 --> 00:11:29.210 position:75%
And that's where we have students think about
open-ended questions and closed-ended questions.

00:11:29.210 --> 00:11:32.500
We use a simple definition of
close-ended as being able to answer

00:11:32.500 --> 00:11:34.760 position:59%
