00:12:47.690 --> 00:12:51.350
So then we have them move on to
look at open-ended questions.

00:12:51.350 --> 00:12:55.310
And ask them to think about the
advantages of open-ended questions.

00:12:55.310 --> 00:12:57.050 position:66%
