abilities at a specific time.

00:24:53.350 --> 00:24:54.950
So let's look at the first one.

00:24:54.950 --> 00:24:57.960
The students begin to think
in many different directions.

00:24:57.960 --> 00:24:59.370
They do divergent thinking.

00:24:59.370 --> 00:25:05.090 position:73%
